  <name>Video Downloader</name>
  <summary>Download videos from websites like YouTube and many others</summary>
  <description>
    <p>
      Download videos from websites with an easy-to-use interface.
      Provides the following features:
    </p>
    <ul>
      <li>Convert videos to MP3</li>
      <li>Supports password-protected and private videos</li>
      <li>Download single videos or whole playlists</li>
      <li>Automatically selects a video format based on your quality demands</li>
    </ul>
    <p>
      Based on youtube-dl.
    </p>
  </description>
